/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁油上去點駁電 最後咪又係一塊板咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPerovskite係化學方式不過唔係油上去噉(雖然簡單)"},{"pid":"0db9e1eb5d48445ade4e8f0af6410b9fa2f2e0e5","tid":168892,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試料於實驗室驗證成功，並唔代表能夠馬上商業量產：<br />\n仲要做多重認證，證明試料能夠高效耐用先至得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPerovskite已經吹奏得夠多"},{"pid":"bd6ca1f9982374b4dfe78df89138db4cd37f5d82","tid":168892,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>效率幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般大陽能板21%，佢依種方法有冇10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n家下太陽能板有咁高轉換率咩?</blockquote><br />\n實驗室內crystalline Si PV已達single-junction上限</blockquote><br />\n仲有背後要跟幾多野? 一大堆叉電, 穩壓器, 分分鐘成百尺空間先夠位放一般家庭用量, 仲未計太陽能板面積, 係香港間屋貼晒係外牆, 都唔知頂唔頂到2粒鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c356e1cfa5ac24611040113e2727f643a5d759","tid":168892,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>效率幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般大陽能板21%，佢依種方法有冇10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n家下太陽能板有咁高轉換率咩?</blockquote><br />\n呢兩年出既板轉換率都高左"},{"pid":"29cc66fff34d321e48c7bfd29ec44cb6d9ac734a","tid":168892,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"高樓大廈一定冇撚用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 澳洲/美國西部/智利就一定好實用<br />\n低密度，多日照時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930b82e306f80b6c4434aabfc26f9908d6a6b0cc","tid":168892,"uid":83